title: Expand the whitelist as part of the Phase 1 BANK distribution
body:
If passed, the Float Protocol BANK token distribution whitelist will be expanded to include

- delegators on Compound
- voters on Yearn
- voters on UMA
- delegators on YAM
- voters and escrowers on Curve
- delegators and voters on Uniswap. 

You must have interacted with one of these protocols before 5th February.

More information can be found here - https://floatprotocol.medium.com/float-protocol-bank-distribution-whitelist-expansion-fd5a84c42356
author: 0x9BdE5b7F8cA82d92b4eC1F4114D59282ec14C65d
